# NETWORK::NETWORK_IS_SIGNED_IN

## Summary
Returns TRUE if the local player is signed into a profile

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether the player is signed into Social Club.
